devdoc.details: Simple payment contract for Banana Fever Dream game Players pay 0.1 APE to play in competitive mode and rank on the leaderboard

clearPayment(address).details: Clear payment status for a player after they finish their game Can be called by anyone, but typically called by the player or leaderboard contract

params._player: Address of the player to clear

hasActivePayment(address).details: Check if a player has an active payment

params._player: Address of the player to check

returns._0: bool True if player has paid and not yet used their credit

playGame().details: Pay to play the game in competitive mode Players must send exactly 0.1 APE

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership to a new address
